    public class Character
extends MovableObject
implements java.lang.Comparable<Character>
    Character in the JavaAdventure Role-Playing Game. Characters have a number of defining characteristics, including:
    • name
    • description
    • weight
    • gender
    • strength
    • dexterity
    • constitution
    • intelligence
    • wisdom
    • charisma
    • health
